# Orphan artifact from some prior session / tool. Self-comment claims it is
# "regenerated by index.html in Phase 2b" per "/docs/data_schemas.md" —
# both of those paths do NOT exist in the repo and no code references
# _index.md. Intended shape (from the file header): a 5-col markdown
# table with columns `| Title | Tier | Path | Updated |`. Investigated
# 2026-04-24; ignored rather than deleted so that IF the tooling the
# comment references ever lands (a Phase 2b indexer writing a
# per-title/tier/path manifest), the file can be re-surfaced without
# having to reconstruct the format from memory. If you add that tooling,
# `git rm` this ignore line at the same time.
/_index.md
